{"tid":1387263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有個心理學家話，我地錯曬喎","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T11:21:23.000Z","uid":34047,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a140703e68a0516a54a5434fe9dd30ee75ada604","tid":1387263,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"#轉發 #呢個要睇<br />\n<br />\n《有個心理學家話，我地錯曬喎》<br />\n<br />\n我係一個心理學家，有啲嘢想講<br />\nRe: 點解8月5號罷工風吹唔起<br />\n<br />\n人係會自動將唔同嘅角色定位<br />\n例如你唔會同公司既老海鮮一齊食飯<br />\n你係普通學生唔會夠膽同籃球隊隊長食飯一樣<br />\n因為係心理上， 你已經自動將自己歸類<br />\n&ldquo;我&ldquo;同&ldquo;佢地&ldquo;唔同，所以行為都會唔同<br />\n<br />\n而家啲示威者叫做後生仔， 勇武派， 有人叫我哋做曱甴 <br />\n普遍社會覺得全部同&ldquo;我&ldquo;無關<br />\n&ldquo;我&ldquo;係和理非，所以我只會遊行，其他社會運動唔關我事<br />\n<br />\n要改變人嘅態度<br />\n必須要由&ldquo;我同示威者唔同&ldquo;<br />\n轉為&ldquo;我地係同一群&ldquo;既心態，先會有機會肯罷工<br />\n<br />\n參照埋第二次世界大戰時用到的宣傳<br />\n可以考慮<br />\n文宣方向<br />\n&ldquo;香港需要你&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我地都係香港人，我願意罷工&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;為了僅餘的自由&ldquo;，加幅罷工圖<br />\n&ldquo;你幫助過前線嗎？&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;為了香港，我們絕不放棄&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;勝利之路&ldquo;<br />\n&ldquo;謝謝你，香港人&ldquo;"},{"pid":"795594514de0116f9b5cc4d08b0aee18ad67097c","tid":1387263,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1791505431090866%2Fposts%2F2420034831571253%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4c2cbeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/</a>"},{"pid":"5a1fd76c7572f6b8327434c21aab1bb899c52274","tid":1387263,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"...唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8105bbfd5a13149a5c463796411bce6fddec0508","tid":1387263,"uid":34047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a1fd76c7572f6b8327434c21aab1bb899c52274","tid":1387263,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"...唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"我諗佢意思係<br />\n就咁寫罷工 啲人會覺得係示威者既事<br />\n但普通人個身份唔係示威者<br />\n<br />\n試下改個字眼"},{"pid":"41c2df2ab16d89cd74df466a27049e619999d259","tid":1387263,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:37:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69c43e9141d7d6219f22d950010485dce42ebdb9","tid":1387263,"uid":125029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:41:07.000Z","msg":"文宣角度&mdash; 從香港、自己人出發宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1398426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1398426</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f25e7a882cf24bcc17e1de57eef7e1a41be9a450","tid":1387263,"uid":296578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:42:54.000Z","msg":"我會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa035e3af642bf00cb4e52fd7a11752ca3bda119","tid":1387263,"uid":122972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:44:58.000Z","msg":"不要說 你班後生仔<br />\n試着說 我地香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bb84a0826f8e3dd9aeadb6a6949e8c5c4ceeb7","tid":1387263,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795594514de0116f9b5cc4d08b0aee18ad67097c","tid":1387263,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1791505431090866%2Fposts%2F2420034831571253%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4c2cbeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:19:37.000Z","msg":"另可參考<br />\n徐緣 十八種建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2179701742127792&amp;id=347912661973385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2179701742127792%26id%3D347912661973385&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=ef12bf42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2179701742127792&amp;id=347912661973385</a><br />\n<br />\n假文宣都話要塞三隧！各位小心！！<br />\n<br />\n義士有生命危險！！8月5號有危險，快入！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392370\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392370</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第11頁有藍絲假文宣合集</strong></span><br />\n補番真文宣source<br />\n5/8 全港大三罷+ 7區開🌼 公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/saveinghkgrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsaveinghkgrp&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=e69998dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/saveinghkgrp</a>"},{"pid":"f991ac73db42ed8c43e474b7d4b1c895c9cf5422","tid":1387263,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"795594514de0116f9b5cc4d08b0aee18ad67097c","tid":1387263,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1791505431090866%2Fposts%2F2420034831571253%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=4c2cbeca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1791505431090866/posts/2420034831571253/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:20:14.000Z","msg":"對中立人士用<br />\n<br />\n崇拜法律的你，每次講起示威者，總是以他們佔領馬路等犯法為由，然後架起了牆，捉著這一點，不再討論，凡是犯法，都是錯，都有問題，是示威者挑起問題，每一次討論，總會帶回到他們犯法點，因為你很信服權威。<br />\n<br />\n那麼，警察呢？警察在這50天裡，也凌駕所有警察通例，基本上不受任何法律約束，連張建宗為警察道歉也錯。<br />\n<br />\n有人仍舊說示威者也傷害警察，不停上載一些片段，証明示威者犯法。崇拜所謂的公平的你，請不要忘記，你認為的示威者犯法，而警方已經檢控了多過50人。然而濫權的警察，50天後，仍舊一個也未有停職、聆訊與受罰。如果要論公平，到底是那一邊永遠是雞蛋？警棍加上水喉戒指、向記者開槍、對示威者頭部及眼部射槍，是不是濫權？為什麼不調查元朗警局拉閘的原因？你追求的權威與公平，可否解釋一下？<br />\n<br />\n如果早在6月16 200萬大遊行前，政府願意成立獨立調查委員會，同時調查警察與示威者，你所追求的公平就可以彰顯。可惜你沒有站在這一方，只是繼續不停沉醉你喜愛的專頁裡，繼續看示威者的「壞」，讓你樂透。<br />\n<br />\n在追求公平的同時，請先問問自己的良心與良知。人心肉造，民眾給消防員的掌聲與給警察的噓聲對比，是人民在大是大非前，最好的証明。<br />\n<br />\n#我每天都看文滙大公港人港地HkG乜乜乜<br />\n#不要說我也只沉迷在黃絲世界<br />\n#看盡只是為了知道不同人有不同想法<br />\n#但唔係要懶中立<br />\n#係大事大非前連沈教授都要站邊<br />\n#其實你扮中立已如王維基所講你已站在高牆一方"},{"pid":"a568dd260a956db184f879e730ce453f397002a8","tid":1387263,"uid":78695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/p6SPF3E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fp6SPF3E.gif&h=6818fdd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85dc71b2586a73b11f5e5f7f4d79283a999c3028","tid":1387263,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:12:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c5ac7cc432488bab7c15e3e718490694bd41d7","tid":1387263,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:17:43.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625f9dcac2d23eb93ef39f139f0530637dd711ef","tid":1387263,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T23:38:26.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b7617064fdb5cc42566ed771ad24677872d6b5","tid":1387263,"uid":48149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}